1. Noble ... reducing poverty and increasing equality of opportunity

Germany suffered great trauma discovering its emperor finally had no clothes despite early popularity
It took a World War for the Germans to learn their folly. What will it take for the bigoted British to learn it?


Brexit = Bigotry and Racism ... and little that is noble persuaded the deluded voters who wanted Brexit.

It has not taken long to show his hand as a priminister leading a failed party and no clue what the vision is for ths parliment. The basis of failure stems from a continuity of failed policies which have brought this country to its knees.


The voters want painful change its not the gravy train as usual.


Its about social justice for the abuse some sectors of this country have suffered under this failed right wing government.
The money for the NHS will be spent on the four main pillars
social care
Restoration of the incomes for the severely disabled and blind whos incomes and compensation are protected by primary legislation not parliment
Primary care
Border control and reducion in immergration
Train our 7.1 million unemployed as medical professionals
Rebuilding of our victorian hospitals to new sites in transport nodes,such as st georges which will be relocated within five years to a new accessable site at Rohampton south London
It will mean disabled trusts for the blind access to pensions,grants, and housing.
We now want civl servants to be criminally responsible for their actions, such as Judges who refuse to allow access to to their courts because they are blind or severely disabled.
New Disability Enforcement Act 2020 which goves lond awaited powers to the police for the attacks on blind people over the last five years.
Removal of means testing, 30 % reduction in train fares, removal of standing charges for all utilities as part of the climate change agenda. Grants for the over eighties and blind for roof mounted solar panel to help with their heating keeping them out of hospital.

Need an elected house of lords from the professions


This parlimnt is about reflating the national economey and social justice for the genocide of the disabled,elderly, and low paid workers.


Johnson has one hundred days to acheive these things otherwise he must go.....Time starts today.
